China’s Tax Change Negative for Oil, Gas Producers’ Ratings, Moody’s Says

-- B y   W e s   G o o d m a n
-- 
2011-09-26T04:03:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/china-s-tax-change-negative-for-oil-gas-producers-ratings-moody-s-says.html
China ’s decision to levy a tax on
resources based on their value and volume is negative for the
debt rating of major Chinese oil and gas producers, Moody’s
Investors Service said it its Weekly Credit Outlook.  “It will increase these companies’ tax bill,” Moody’s
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
